      "span_text": "In situ stress measurements were done using a multiple-beam optical stress sensor (MOSS) during deposition of lms (see the schematic in Fig. 1 and ESI S-1 † for more), details of which are mentioned in our previous publication.  These YSZ lms are cubic (8 mol% or 15 wt%).",
